the house of an Oakland Tribune reporter
an article about Meehan 's department 's response
Peter Cukor , 67 , and his wife , Andrea
the police department was responding only to Priority 1
the police union called for an independent investigation
the most intimidating of all types of prior restraint or censorship that can be exercised
Jim Ewert , general counsel of the California Newspaper Publishers ' Association
